Day 6 - AI Resume Optimizer
Objective
Learn how AI can improve resume quality, ATS compatibility, and recruiter readability.

Prompt Used
You are an expert ATS Resume Optimizer and Technical Recruiter.

Analyze my resume and provide:

ATS Score (out of 100)
Strengths of the resume
Weaknesses and improvement areas
Missing keywords for AI, Cybersecurity, Data Analytics, and Software Engineering roles
Formatting recommendations
Content recommendations
Project recommendations
Skills recommendations
Then generate an optimized one-page ATS-friendly resume that:

Keeps all information truthful
Improves readability
Improves recruiter appeal
Improves ATS compatibility
Highlights projects, technical skills, and achievements
Uses strong action verbs
Is suitable for internships and entry-level technical roles
Finally provide:

Estimated ATS score after optimization
Top improvements made
Original Resume Analysis
I uploaded my resume and requested an ATS analysis.

Strengths Identified
Strong technical background
Relevant academic projects
Interest in AI and Cybersecurity
Good educational foundation
Areas for Improvement
More ATS keywords
Stronger action verbs
Better project descriptions
Improved formatting and readability
ATS Score
Before Optimization
ATS Score - 54

After Optimization
Improved ATS Score - 91

Resume Optimization Results
Claude generated an optimized one-page resume with:

Better ATS compatibility
Improved keyword optimization
Stronger project descriptions
Better formatting
More recruiter-friendly language
Key Learnings
ATS systems rely heavily on relevant keywords.
Projects should demonstrate impact, not just tasks.
Quantifiable achievements improve recruiter interest.
Resume structure affects ATS parsing.
AI can significantly improve resume presentation while keeping information truthful.
Biggest Takeaway
A resume should be optimized for both ATS systems and human recruiters. AI can help identify weaknesses, improve keyword coverage, and create a more professional presentation of existing skills and experiences.
